# I have successfully moved to the nearest iron ore patch.
# 
# Now, I will harvest more iron ore to ensure that I have enough for the stone furnace to continue smelting.

harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.IronOre), quantity=10)  # Harvesting 10 iron ore from the iron ore patch.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check the updated inventory after harvesting.
